title: American Greed Season 8 - EPS 1-13 !
description:
This the American greed season 8 EPISODES 1-13.

The files are from various trackers and http downloads. Quality is mostly 720p.

Hope you enjoy and learn a valuable lesson from all these people who lost all their money. Don't be greedy and put your investments in many places because you never know what kind of bad luck you are going to have in this world.
